Source: yavdr-hostwakeup
Section: net
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Lars Hanisch <dvb@flensrocker.de>
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 7), python-avahi
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: https://github.com/flensrocker/hostwakeup

Package: yavdr-hostwakeup
Architecture: any
Depends: python3-avahi, python3-netifaces, python-gi-dev
Recommends: avahi-daemon
Description: A network services for waking up hosts
 This service will collect hostnames and their MACs from other
 stations on the LAN running the service. Any program can wakeup
 any station just knowing the hostname.

